          "Homeostasis",
          "Metabolism",
          "Autotroph",
          "Heterotroph"
        ],
        "teacherMoves": [
          "Use the 'Car' analogy to explain energy input."
        ],
        "examples": [
          "A car needs fuel; a human needs food. Both need maintenance (repair)."
        ],
